Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.15,0:00:08.07,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}Zankoku na tenshi no you ni 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:16.00,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}shounen yo shinwa ni nare
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:30.51,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}Aoi kaze ga ima mune no doa wo tataitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:38.29,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}watashi dake wo tada mitsumete hohoenderu anata
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:45.33,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}Sotto fureru mono motomeru koto ni muchuu de
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:53.17,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}unmei sae mada shiranai itaikena hitomi
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:59.49,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}Dakedo itsuka kizuku deshou sono senaka ni wa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:07.61,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}Haruka mirai mezasu tame no hane ga aru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:15.58,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}Zankoku na tenshi no teze madobe kara yagate tobitatsu
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:23.08,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}hotobashiru atsui patosu de omoide wo uragiru nara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:26.90,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}Kono sora wo daite kagayaku 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:30.84,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}{\fad(200,100)}shounen yo shinwa ni nare
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.15,0:00:08.07,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}Como um anjo cruel, 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:16.00,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}seja uma lenda, jovem garoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.56,0:00:30.51,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}Um vento azul está batendo na porta do seu coração,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.51,0:00:38.29,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}e, no entanto, você está apenas me olhando sorrindo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.75,0:00:45.33,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}Algo toca suavemente, você está tão concentrado em procurá-lo,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.57,0:00:53.17,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}que ainda nem consegue ver o seu destino, com olhos tão inocentes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.17,0:00:59.49,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}Mas um dia, eu acho, você vai descobrir que o que está nas suas costas.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.60,0:01:07.61,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}São asas para voar em direção a um futuro distante.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.24,0:01:15.58,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}A tese do anjo cruel logo voará pela janela,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:23.08,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}com uma paixão ardente e crescente, se você trair suas memórias.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.20,0:01:26.90,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}Abrace este universo e brilhe,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.90,0:01:30.84,NGE - Romaji,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\an2\blur2}garoto, torne-se uma lenda!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,2015 A.D.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.99,0:01:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At 12:30 p.m. today, a special state{\i}\N{\i1}of emergency has been declared{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the Toukai region{\i}\N{\i1}and the surrounding mid-Kanto area.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.63,0:02:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All residents, proceed to your designated{\i}\N{\i1}evacuation shelter immediately.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.21,0:02:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat, at 12:30 p.m. today,{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.84,0:02:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}a special state of emergency{\i}\N{\i1}has been declared{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.26,0:02:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}for the Toukai region{\i}\N{\i1}and the surrounding mid-Kanto area.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.31,0:02:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Proceed to your designated...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I lose track of him\Nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.23,0:02:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All phone lines{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}are currently disabled due to{\i}\N{\i1}the special state of emergency.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.74,0:02:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't reach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.87,0:02:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.37,0:02:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's that, then.\NMight as well head to a shelter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.07,0:03:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unidentified object is continuing{\i}\N{\i1}its approach to this facility.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.37,0:03:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We have visual on target.{\i}\N{\i1}Sending to main screen.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.29,0:03:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there's no doubt about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.29,0:03:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All missiles, direct hit!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.54,0:04:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry! Been waiting long?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.18,0:04:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Target unfazed. It is continuing{\i}\N{\i1}to advance towards Tokyo-3.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.77,0:04:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Local air units are unable{\i}\N{\i1}to slow its advance!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.98,0:04:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is total war. Launch all units\Nfrom Atsugi and Iruma as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.23,0:04:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Commit everything we have!\NCrush the target at all costs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.96,0:04:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This makes no sense!\NThose were direct hits!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.71,0:04:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Our armored battalion has been wiped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Guided munitions, bombs,\Nand artillery are having no effect.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.01,0:05:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! This kind of firepower\Nisn't getting us anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.55,0:05:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,An A.T. Field?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Standard weapons\Nwill be useless against the Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir. We'll deploy it\Naccording to plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.82,0:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,They wouldn't...\NThey're gonna use an N2 land mine?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.62,0:05:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but your services\Nweren't required this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.35,0:05:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shock wave incoming.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:57.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.73,0:06:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but I got some sand in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.19,0:06:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad to hear it. Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.62,0:06:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.75,0:06:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.\NI couldn't have done it without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.04,0:06:20.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I should be thanking {\i1}you{\i},\NMs. Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.09,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Call me Misato, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nice to meet you, Shinji Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.51,0:06:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Target's current status?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.02,0:06:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Target status unknown, EMI too strong.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.93,0:06:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw that explosion!\NIt must have been obliterated!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.81,0:06:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sensors coming back online.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.44,0:06:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Energy readings at ground zero!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.78,0:06:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Visual feed back online.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.49,0:06:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That was our ace in the hole...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,God-damned monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.17,0:07:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, not to worry.\NHis protection has top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.93,0:07:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So have the car shuttle train standing by.\NThe direct service line.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.85,0:07:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Well, I {\i1}am{\i} the one\Nwho said I would go meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.48,0:07:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm keeping my word. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man, what a day!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.24,0:07:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just had this car restored,{\i}\N{\i1}and it's trashed already!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.49,0:07:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Repair fees, on top of another{\i}\N{\i1}33 months of car payments...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.87,0:07:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Plus, my best outfit is ruined!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Um, Ms. Misato?\N-{\i1}I got all decked out for today...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-Excuse me, Ms. Misato?\N-Yes, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it okay for you to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.01,0:07:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.34,0:07:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is an emergency!\NI had to get the car moving, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.10,0:07:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I might not look it,\Nbut I'm an international civil servant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.60,0:07:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's perfectly legit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.52,0:07:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.27,0:08:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, lighten up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.15,0:08:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For a kid with such a cute face,\Nyou sure are uptight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.86,0:08:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops! Are you mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry! You're a boy, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.70,0:08:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, you seem a bit childish\Nfor someone your age, Ms. Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.84,0:08:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,As we predicted, it's regenerating?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If it couldn't, it would be worthless\Nas a standalone weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.51,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Very impressive. It's even capable\Nof enhancing its abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.56,0:08:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's getting smarter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.77,0:08:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only a matter of time\Nbefore it resumes its advance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gates closing. Please stay clear.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.44,0:08:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Special Agency Nerv?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.15,0:08:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. It's a secret organization\Ndirectly attached to the UN.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.87,0:08:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,My father works here, doesn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.62,0:08:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup. Do you know\Nwhat your father does here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.71,0:09:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,A teacher told me that he has\Nthe important job of protecting humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.67,0:09:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,As of this moment, you have been\Ngiven command over this operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's see what you can do.\N-Understood, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.31,0:09:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, I'll admit that our ordnance\Nis ineffective against the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.31,0:09:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you defeat it, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.27,0:09:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what Nerv is for.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let us down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Target status has not changed.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Current intercept capacity is at 7.5%.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.12,0:09:41.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The UN Forces have given up, then?\NWhat do you intend to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll activate Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.71,0:09:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01? But there's no pilot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.55,0:09:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a problem.\NThe spare pilot will arrive shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we be going to see my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.27,0:10:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Father...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.23,0:10:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! Did your father\Nsend you any ID forms?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.40,0:10:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.16,0:10:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.07,0:10:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,COME HERE!\N-GENDOH IKARI
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Read through this, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.87,0:10:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,"Welcome to Nerv"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.08,0:10:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My father's work...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I supposed to do something at Nerv?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.13,0:10:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,There has to be. Otherwise,\NFather wouldn't have written to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.26,0:10:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. Dealing with your father\Nisn't your strong suit, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.68,0:10:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.23,0:10:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,-A bona fide Geo-front!\N-That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.57,0:10:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Over there is our secret base,\NNerv headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.36,0:10:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The key to rebuilding the world,\Nand the last bastion of humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.58,0:11:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.88,0:11:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I could swear it was this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.38,0:11:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Closed Central Dogma passages{\i}\N{\i1}will remain...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Wearing skirts in this place\Nis a bad idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.84,0:11:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder where Ritsuko went?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I don't have my bearings yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We passed through here already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.23,0:11:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not to worry!\NNerv has systems for this very situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Paging Project E. Dir., Dr. Ritsuko Akagi{\i}\N{\i1}of Technology Division Section 1.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Dr. Ritsuko Akagi.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.20,0:11:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please contact Capt. Misato Katsuragi{\i}\N{\i1}of Operations Division Section 1.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.95,0:11:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't believe it.\NShe's lost again, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops! Hi, Ritsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Where have you been, Capt. Katsuragi?\NWe're short on both manpower and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.48,0:12:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep. He's the Third Children\Nreported by the Marduk Institute.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.86,0:12:11.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.02,0:12:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.11,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's another way\Nthat he takes after his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A total lack of charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.24,0:12:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of things here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.29,0:12:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't seen each other\Nin three years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.67,0:12:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Deputy Commander,\Nthe target has begun moving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.34,0:12:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. All personnel\Nto condition one battle stations.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I repeat, condition one battle stations!{\i}\N{\i1}Prepare for ground intercept.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.84,0:12:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hear that?\N-This sounds bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.47,0:12:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how is Unit 01?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's being cooled down\Nin its Type B Configuration.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.02,0:12:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It that thing really going to work?\NIt's hasn't worked once, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.98,0:12:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The odds of a successful activation\Nare 0.000000001%.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.49,0:13:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Calling it the 0-9 System\Nwas certainly appropriate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that mean it won't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.70,0:13:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be rude. It's not 0%.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, numerically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.29,0:13:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well. We don't exactly have\Nthe luxury of accepting failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.47,0:13:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A face? A giant robot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't find this\Nin the orientation book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.11,0:13:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the ultimate multipurpose decisive\Ncombat weapons system created by man.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.19,0:13:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The Artificial Human Evangelion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Unit 01 of the series.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Built in complete secrecy,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.58,0:13:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,this is mankind's very last trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.29,0:13:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-This is part of my father's work?\N{\i1}-Correct.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.12,0:13:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.92,0:13:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.67,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch the Eva?\NBut Unit 00 is still grounded!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.43,0:14:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you want to use Unit 01?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:10.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait just a second!\NRei's in no condition for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.77,0:14:16.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got no pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.07,0:14:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.53,0:14:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.57,0:14:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Shinji Ikari.\N-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to pilot it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But it took even Rei Ayanami seven months\Nto synchronize with her Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.87,0:14:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,He literally just got here!\NHe couldn't possibly do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.54,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All I ask is that he sit in the cockpit.\NNothing more.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Repelling that Angel\Nis our number one priority right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,For that, we need anyone capable of\Nsynchronizing with an Eva to try,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,however remote the chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.89,0:14:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't need to tell you this,\NCapt. Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.23,0:14:57.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Father... Why did you send for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For the reason you're thinking.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.82,0:15:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So you want me to get inside this\Nand fight that thing out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.20,0:15:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.36,0:15:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to do that!\NWhy send for me after all this time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you left me\Nbecause you didn't need me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.66,0:15:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I do now, so I sent for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.42,0:15:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But why me?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.42,0:15:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's impossible for anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.46,0:15:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It is for me, too. I've never seen\Nor heard of this thing before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.80,0:15:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't possibly do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.97,0:15:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Learn how.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.14,0:15:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's... That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can pilot this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.23,0:15:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to pilot it, do it.\NOtherwise, get out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard must have figured out\Nwhere we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.08,0:16:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinji, we don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. I just got here! This is crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, Shinji. Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.60,0:16:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away! Not from your father,\Nand especially not from yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.32,0:16:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! But there's no way I can do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.37,0:16:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuyutsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Wake up Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is she viable?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,She isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.46,0:16:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Understood.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.42,0:16:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-Rei?\N{\i1}-Yes?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The backup isn't working out.\NI need you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.22,0:16:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes, sir.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Rewrite Unit 01's core system\Nfor Rei! Reactivate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.98,0:17:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger. Suspending current tasks{\i}\N{\i1}and initiating reactivation.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.94,0:17:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I knew it... No one wants me.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.61,0:17:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}The Eva moved!{\i}\N-{\i1}What the hell?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.16,0:17:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Its right arm broke free{\i}\N{\i1}of its restraints!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:18:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! That can't be!\NIt doesn't have an entry plug inserted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.54,0:18:02.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's incapable of moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It reacted without any\Ninterface connection?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.13,0:18:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Or was it trying... to protect him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,This {\i1}will{\i} work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Don't run away.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.83,0:18:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it. I'll be the pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Cooling cycle complete!{\i}\N-{\i1}Right arm reattachment complete.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All gear inside cage{\i}\N{\i1}is in docked position.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shutdown signal plug extraction complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.22,0:18:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger. Inserting entry plug.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.85,0:19:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Plug locked in position.{\i}\N-{\i1}Initiating level one connection.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.03,0:19:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Flooding entry plug.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.86,0:19:18.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is this stuff?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.37,0:19:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry,\Nonce your lungs are filled with LCL,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.41,0:19:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,it will feed oxygen\Ndirectly into your bloodstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll get used to it in no time.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.01,0:19:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is so gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal with it! You're a big boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,-{\i1}Main power connection complete!{\i}\N-{\i1}Feeding power to all circuits!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.64,0:19:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.72,0:19:44.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Initiating level two contact.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A10 nerve connection, status green.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cognitive configuration{\i}\N{\i1}base rules set to Japanese.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Initial contact shows all green.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Opening bilateral circuit.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.24,0:20:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Synchronization rate at 41.3%.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.41,0:20:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,-Amazing...\N-Harmonics are all at normal levels.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,-No signs of a runaway.\N-We're good to go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.38,0:20:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Prepare for launch!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Release lockdown bolt no. 01!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Release confirmed!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.39,0:20:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Initiating umbilical bridge retraction!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.64,0:20:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Release lockdown bolt no. 02!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Retracting primary restraining frame.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.40,0:20:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Removing secondary{\i}\N{\i1}restraining frame, as well.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.36,0:20:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Disengaging safety systems one through 15.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Internal power source, fully charged.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.87,0:20:45.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}External power source connecter{\i}\N{\i1}shows green.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.04,0:20:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger. Transport Eva-01 to launch bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.47,0:21:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch path clear! All stations green!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.89,0:21:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch preparations complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.93,0:21:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.02,0:21:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,-Do we have a go, sir?\N-Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.06,0:21:16.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Unless we defeat the Angels,\Nhumanity has no future.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.15,0:21:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Ikari, you're really sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.74,0:21:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.78,0:21:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji... don't die.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.03,0:22:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,TO BE CONTINUED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.09,0:23:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,NEXT EPISODE
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.01,0:23:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The Eva defeats the Angel,{\i}\N{\i1}but that was just the beginning.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shinji runs away from his father.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.73,0:23:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Misato's arrogance makes her{\i}\N{\i1}decide to try to save him.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.02,0:23:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Next episode! "Unfamiliar Ceilings"!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.40,0:23:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tune in next time{\i}\N{\i1}for lots more fan service!{\i}
